name: VSError.Code
desc: Error codes in the framework error domain.

items.name: case accessNotGranted
items.desc: The user hasn’t granted access to their subscription information.

items.name: case invalidVerificationToken
items.desc: The user’s subscription provider rejected the verification token that the app sent with the request.

items.name: case providerRejected
items.desc: The user’s subscription provider didn’t allow the request to proceed.

items.name: case serviceTemporarilyUnavailable
items.desc: The request failed due to a timeout or unreachable host, but a subsequent attempt might succeed.

items.name: case unsupported
items.desc: The provider doesn’t support the feature the user requested in the device’s current region.

items.name: case unsupportedProvider
items.desc: The system doesn’t support the user’s subscription provider.
